Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:52.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}and I’m alright
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.74,0:22:53.12,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’ll be alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:55.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}yeah I hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.80,0:22:56.34,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I care about you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:23:01.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}伸びた髪を風がからかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:04.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}全部意味があるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}立ち止まった日々も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:13.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今さらわかってあなたに追いついたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:17.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ほら　この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:25.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}見えなかったものが　どうして　溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:31.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}せめて　会いたいよなんて言わないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:37.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ねえ　今日だけは思い出していいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:43.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}だからあなたとまた巡りあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:49.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}もう迷わない今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.08,0:23:52.28,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Anytime anywhere yah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:54.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どこにいても
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.52,0:23:57.67,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Anytime anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:57.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑ってみせて
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.16,0:24:01.96,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’ll be there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:24:00.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}目を閉じれば　いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:03.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}絶対なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:06.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつでも届いているから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:09.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その涙だって大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:19.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’m whispering our lullaby for you to come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:52.04,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我还好
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.74,0:22:53.12,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:55.08,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我听到了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.80,0:22:56.34,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:23:01.74,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}轻风在长发间嬉戏着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:04.02,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}这一切都有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.31,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}包括那些驻足不前的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:13.40,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}到如今我也终于能理解并追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:17.70,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如果不是这双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:25.13,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}那么这么多看不到的事物 又如何满溢出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:31.41,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}至少 我不会说出想见到你这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:37.08,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我说 只有今天让我追忆你可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:43.11,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}所以 如果我们能再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:49.02,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我一定不再会迷茫 而是选择当下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:54.84,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.08,0:23:52.28,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}随时 随地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:57.67,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我都会为你欢笑
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.52,0:23:57.67,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}随时 随地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:24:00.66,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}每当合上双眼 总是
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.16,0:24:01.96,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:03.49,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就算没有绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:06.47,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也总能够传达到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:09.67,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就算落泪也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.97,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为黎明一定会来临
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:19.24,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我会为你的归来轻声歌唱着我们摇篮曲
